name: Well Travelled
description:
In Well Travelled, you've just returned from a trip around the world! As you review photos from the trip, can you correctly recall which countries you were in?

The objective of the game is to correctly identify which country is visible in the displayed photos. Try to guess all 5 countries correctly!

I created this game for Trijam #186. The theme is "I am a traveller."  It took about 7 hours of active development time to complete. 

Built With
  • Vanilla JS
  • Visual Studio Code
  • TinyPNG for image compression

Third Party Assets

  • Pixel Space Background Generator
  • Pixel Planet Generator
  • All country images are from https://unsplash.com/.  Find all the specific URLs here: https://github.com/townsean/trijam-186/blob/main/scripts/countries.json
